author: lundblad
msg: On the nonxml-entries branch: Improve error handling when dealing with
corrupt entries files.  Allow unknown fields at the end of each entry line.
(read_str, read_bool, read_val): Replace asserts with real error checking.
(read_entries): Wrap errors from parsing the entries with line and file
information.  Ignore text at the end of an entry line for extensibility.
